function pts=ellipse_data(object,imNo)
%ELLIPSE_DATA Return realistic data for the ellipse fitting problem.
%
%pts=ellipse_data(object,imNo)
%object  - 1 (femoral head), 2 (cup), 3 (cup opening), 4 (mystery).
%imNo    - 1 or 2. Image to select hip femoral head projection points from.
%pts     - 2xN matrix with measured points as columns. Unit: pixels.

